:: 2a. Your soul is gonna burn in a Lake of Fire! {"position":"725,300","size":"100,100"}
{<h1>Yes!</h1>
<br><h4>You wanna know the truth, son... 
<br>Oh I'll tell you the truth! 
<br>Your soul is gonna burn in a lake of fire</h4>
