</audio>
<br><h2>Iron Maiden!
<br>Can I play with madness!</h2>
<br>Remember, You already sold your soul and signed an autograph.
<br>That's madness!
<br>
<br>Let's proceed to next question...
<br>[[what do you wanna do with your life?]]
<br>}


