:: We start from HERE {"position":"600,1025","size":"100,100"}
{<p>You came from the future...
<br>Your musical knowledge is inspiring and is always improving
<br>You learned time travel can be achieved through timeless songs
<br>As you already realized, the key thing is to sound
<br>This ressonance connect us.</p>
