---
<br>[[Look for something new...]]
<br><br>
---
<div class="div-blue">
Many times I've been a traveller
<br>I looked for something new...
<br>In days of old when nights were cold
<br>I wandered without you
<br>Those days I thought my eyes had seen you standing near
